Hey there!
We are back with some more info on DSC WOW, so that you can have more than 'just a peek' into what it really is! (Don't worry, we still have some gems kept hidden in our pockets.😉)

Well the trailer must have quenched some of your curiosity filled thirst. No?

Okay, so let's share some interesting facts with you guys!👻

Did you notice that the entire video has some specific theme to it? No? Y'all, keep up!😪

Well, the entire video revolves around Google's colour palette, i.e., red, yellow, blue and green. 

But you may wonder why only these colours?
Well, according to colour psychology, these colours represent ambition, intellect, integrity, balance and growth, respectively. 

And just like these colours, DSC WOW integrates in itself all of these qualities as well, both figuratively and literally!

So are you ready to be enthralled by these colours?

Then JOIN US this DECEMBER! @dsc.wow

node.text:
Here's your chance to become a member of GDSC JSSSTU chapter and enjoy all the perks!
Swipe left for a detailed guide ✨

Perks of being a member of GDSC! 🌻

• GDSC will be your guiding light if you are aiming to grow your knowledge of Developer Technologies, through many peer to peer workshops and events. 🙌🏼 

• You will be gaining relevant industry experience by solving problems for local organizations with technology-based solutions, how cool is that! 🥳

• You will not only be building your professional and personal networks but also get access to resources exclusively from Google Developers Student Clubs - You definitely don't want to miss out on that! 💥

• Best part? GDSC mainly focuses on students'
Professional Growth -> We help you become a leader who aspires to gain training and technical knowledge 

Network Growth -> You will be part of a global network of student leaders, community organizers, industry experts, and Googlers to gain mentorship 💯

Community Learning -> We are dedicated to providing support to help educate and expand our community online and in person. 👩🏼‍💻👨🏼‍💻

• GDSC membership is completely free of cost and full of pros; you will be updated with technical news and updates on a regular basis. 🔔

We standby our motto
Connect Learn Grow and welcome you all to our community! 🌻

node.text:
You're going to love this! Here's your chance to get a headstart on an enlightening and forthcoming skill ✨

Hang on to your seats as GDSC JSSSTU brings to you a two day workshop on Machine learning,
EXPLORE ML! 🤖

Why ML? 🤔
It allows the user to feed an immense amount of data and makes data driven decisions based on the input.

Basically, the ability to automatically learn and improve from past experiences.

Pre-requisites: Basics of Python and enthusiasm is all you need 🤩

You don't wanna miss out on this!

Don't forget the important dates: 27th November, 2:30 PM to 5:30 PM and 28th of November, 11 AM to 5:30 PM

Link will be live on 24th November, 7 PM

node.text:
Wanting to learn big data, machine learning and application development? 

Here's the sign you've been looking for! 🙌🏻

GDSC brings to you the annual 30 Days of Google Cloud event from the 27th of September to the 27th of October 2021. 

📌 On the successful completion of this event, participants will stand a chance to win goodies like laptop bags, customized T-shirts, Google Cloud sticker packs and many more exciting stuff. 

📌 The benefits don't end here! Completing the tracks will also get you a certificate of participation and cool badges which can be added to your resume or LinkedIn profile. 

Facing issues along the way? No worries! 
We have our campus facilitator Poorvi Shetty who is specially trained on Google Cloud to help everyone with their queries.

📌 Only 50K registrations will be available across India, so go to guide given in bio and complete the steps required to grab a seat‼️
